text: Mokdad Sifi (; born 21 April 1940) is an Algerian politician. Sifi was Head of Government of Algeria from 11 April 1994 to 31 December 1995. In 1999, he unsuccessfully ran for President of Algeria."The candidates who pulled out" BBC News, 15 April 1999 ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Algeria
